        <h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 3.5rem; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 15px;">
            <span id="text-left" style="display: inline-block;">Welcome to</span>
            <span id="text-right" style="display: inline-block; font-family: 'Titan One', cursive; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: normal;">Jom<span style="color: #FF9800;">KL!</span></span>
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #f8f9fa; text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); margin-bottom: 30px;">
            Discover the culture and landmarks of Kuala Lumpur through interactive learning.
        </p>
